('The Irishman', '2019', 'Martin Scorsese, Robert De Niro, Jane Rosenthal, and Emma Tillinger Koskoff', 'Nominee', '2019', '209', 'Biography,Crime,Drama', '7.8', '349303', 'In the 1950s, truck driver Frank Sheeran gets involved with Russell Bufalino and his Pennsylvania crime family. As Sheeran climbs the ranks to become a top hit man, he also goes to work for Jimmy Hoffa -- a powerful Teamster tied to organized crime.', 'An epic gangster drama that earns its extended runtime, The Irishman finds Martin Scorsese revisiting familiar themes to poignant, funny, and profound effect.', 'R'),
